description: Feel free to book INSTANTLY. You can check-in 24 hours a day. My place is on Cedar Street in the heart of Beacon Hill. One of the nicest streets in Boston. The apartment is a beautiful duplex with 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Everything was renovated recently! You’ll love my place because of the people, the neighborhood, and the ambiance. My place is good for couples, families, tourists, and business travelers. Check out our other properties here: https://www.airbnb.com/users/91548283/listings This is a quiet and peaceful part of Boston. Spaces are charming, cozy and quintessential Boston - feels like 1890 in this part of town. Enjoy the history with all the creature comforts of modern day. The apartment is a duplex with 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Both bedrooms have a queen sized bed. The living is very spacious and even has a fireplace. Couch is super comfortable and is also a pull out bed (fit for 2). Brand new tv with cable.  The kitchen is equipped with all stainless steel applianc
name: Gorgeous 2BR/2BA Duplex in Beacon Hill

description: The guest house is close to: Equinox West Hollywood Barry's Bootcamp Chateau Marmont Cecconi's Pacific Design Center Melrose Retail Stores Soho House Alfred's Coffee La Brea Tarpits LACMA EarthBar Craig's Universal Studios Hollywood Runyon Canyon My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers. Luxury decorated unit adjacent (guest house) to a large modern home. No expense was spared in decorating this until to look just like the large modern home. Same wood floors, marble bathroom, granite kitchen, large-scale art, large TV with surround sound.  Working professionals will enjoy the glass desk with large monitor you can plug your laptop into. Wifi, cable and everything you need. Listing for access to the guest house only. Back yard and pool is gated off for large modern home only. Please do not disturb those in the house. I always have my phone unless traveling. This neighborhood is one of the best in LA. EVERYTHING is walking distance OR a short uberX away. Less

description: Private room in a three bedroom apartment in NYC's best neighborhood. The bedroom is a bright corner room with two large windows and direct access to a large rooftop patio. It is on the opposite side of the apartment as the other two bedrooms, offering some privacy. The room has closet space and plenty of room for a queen-sized bed. Located 3 blocks from the subway, 1 block from the water, surrounded by great restaurants, bars, and shops. The perfect base for your NYC stay! Newly-renovated apartment with three bedroom, incredible amounts of natural light (10 total windows!), a full kitchen with brand new appliances, a washer/dryer unit, and spacious living room with large, L-shaped couch. Easy access on the second floor of the building. Guests have access to the kitchen, bathroom, living area, and their own private rooftop patio. description: Our cozy, pet friendly one bedroom apartment/loft with balkony is located in trendy neighborhood - Studio City, close to Ventura blvd with plenty great bars, restaurants, cool little boutiques and beautiful golf course next to our home. Everything is  3 minutes distance by car and 15 minutes walking distance. Comfortable, with balcony, fool kitchen with all the spices ( we love to cook), plenty of sun all day long, big windows, walking distance to bars and restaurants, 2 blocks away from beautiful golf course and lots of amazing  canyons for hiking 15 minutes away by car. Our home is your home so you have access to everything :) We also have nice BBQ on balcony:) As many times they need us :) Beautiful, peaceful, green, young, fun, walking distance to great bars and restaurants. Great options for hiking. For all  animals lovers, our next door neighbor is Cesar Millan :) Bus, über, Lift
